{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881919008,"sessionID":"ses_2853474a4ffeJw71Wrl49XNHYW","part":{"id":"prt_d7ace05d5001BXXCDlfwgfmF32","messageID":"msg_d7acdf68b0012trpjr0TCBa33D","sessionID":"ses_2853474a4ffeJw71Wrl49XNHYW","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n> **Module:** `cmd`  \n> **Language:** Go  \n> **Size:** M  \n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)  \n> **Base Spec:** project.md, deployment/design.md\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nAR-019 implements the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components:\n1. **agentd** - Idle cleanup controller binary\n2. **router** - Session routing proxy binary  \n3. **workload-manager** - Sandbox orchestration binary\n4. **picod** - Sandbox daemon binary\n\nEach binary SHALL parse CLI flags, initialize configuration, wire dependencies, start the respective service, and handle graceful shutdown via OS signals.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.1 — Common Infrastructure\n\n### 4.1.1 Signal Handling Package\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.1.1.1 | Create `pkg/common/signal` package | Directory exists | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.1.2 | Implement `SetupSignalHandler()` returning `<-chan struct{}` | Function exists and compiles | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.1.3 | Handle SIGINT and SIGTERM | Test with `kill -INT` and `kill -TERM` | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.1.4 | Implement graceful timeout handling | Channel closes after signal received | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** `pkg/common/signal` package with signal handling utilities.\n\n### 4.1.2 Version Package\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.1.2.1 | Create `pkg/common/version` package | Directory exists | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.2.2 | Define `var Version = \"dev\"` for ldflags injection | Variable exists and exported | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.2.3 | Add `PrintVersion(binaryName string)` function | Prints \"binaryName version: {Version}\" | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.2.4 | Add `--version` flag support pattern | Document in spec | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Version package for consistent version reporting across binaries.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.2 — Agentd Binary Entry Point\n\n### 4.2.1 Directory and File Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.1.1 | Ensure `cmd/agentd/` directory exists | `ls cmd/agentd/` succeeds | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.1.2 | Create `cmd/agentd/main.go` | File compiles | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.2.2 Flag Parsing\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.2.1 | Define `--kubeconfig` flag (string, default: \"\") | `flag.String(\"kubeconfig\", \"\", \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.2.2 | Define `--sync-period` flag (duration, default: 5m) | `flag.Duration(\"sync-period\", 5*time.Minute, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.2.3 | Define `--graceful-timeout` flag (duration, default: 30s) | `flag.Duration(\"graceful-timeout\", 30*time.Second, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.2.4 | Call `flag.Parse()` in main | Flags parse correctly | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.2.3 Manager Construction\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.3.1 | Import `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager` | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.3.2 | Import `k8s.io/client-go/tools/clientcmd` | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.3.3 | Build Kubernetes config (in-cluster or from kubeconfig) | Config builds without error | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.3.4 | Create manager with Scheme containing sandboxv1alpha1 | Manager creates successfully | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.3.5 | Disable metrics server (`BindAddress: \"0\"`) | Manager starts without metrics | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.3.6 | Disable health probe server (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`) | Manager starts without probes | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.2.4 Reconciler Setup\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.4.1 | Import `pkg/agentd` reconciler package | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.4.2 | Create reconciler instance with manager client | Reconciler creates | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.4.3 | Setup reconciler with manager using `ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy` | Controller registered | 0.5h |\n\n### 4.2.5 Graceful Shutdown\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.5.1 | Set up signal handler for SIGINT/SIGTERM | `signal.SetupSignalHandler()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.5.2 | Start manager in goroutine | `go mgr.Start(ctx)` | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.5.3 | Wait for signal then gracefully stop | `<-signalChan` triggers shutdown | 0.25h |\n| 4.2.5.4 | Implement graceful timeout handling | Shutdown completes within timeout | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** `cmd/agentd/main.go` compiles and runs with flag parsing.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.3 — Router Binary Entry Point\n\n### 4.3.1 Directory and File Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.1.1 | Ensure `cmd/router/` directory exists | `ls cmd/router/` succeeds | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.1.2 | Create `cmd/router/main.go` | File compiles | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.3.2 Flag Parsing\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.2.1 | Define `--port` flag (int, default: 8080) | `flag.Int(\"port\", 8080, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2.2 | Define `--debug` flag (bool, default: false) | `flag.Bool(\"debug\", false, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2.3 | Define `--redis-addr` flag (string, required) | Flag defined, validation in code | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2.4 | Define `--workload-manager` flag (string, required) | Flag defined, validation in code | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2.5 | Define `--graceful-timeout` flag (duration, default: 30s) | `flag.Duration(\"graceful-timeout\", 30*time.Second, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.2.6 | Validate required flags after `flag.Parse()` | Exits with error if missing | 0.5h |\n\n### 4.3.3 Server Construction\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.3.1 | Import `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.3.2 | Create Gin router instance | `gin.New()` or `gin.Default()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.3.3 | Set Gin mode based on `--debug` flag | `gin.SetMode(gin.DebugMode/ReleaseMode)` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.3.4 | Import `pkg/router` package | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.3.5 | Wire router handlers and middleware | Routes registered | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.3.6 | Create HTTP server with configured port | `&http.Server{Addr: fmt.Sprintf(\":%d\", *port)}` | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.3.4 Graceful Shutdown\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.4.1 | Start HTTP server in goroutine | `go server.ListenAndServe()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.4.2 | Set up signal handler | `signal.SetupSignalHandler()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.3.4.3 | Implement graceful shutdown with timeout | `server.Shutdown(ctx)` with timeout | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** `cmd/router/main.go` compiles and runs with flag parsing.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.4 — Workload Manager Binary Entry Point\n\n### 4.4.1 Directory and File Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.1.1 | Ensure `cmd/workload-manager/` directory exists | `ls cmd/workload-manager/` succeeds | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.1.2 | Create `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` | File compiles | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.4.2 Flag Parsing\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.2.1 | Define `--port` flag (int, default: 8080) | `flag.Int(\"port\", 8080, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.2 | Define `--kubeconfig` flag (string, default: \"\") | `flag.String(\"kubeconfig\", \"\", \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.3 | Define `--redis-addr` flag (string, required) | Flag defined, validation in code | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.4 | Define `--default-image` flag (string, default: \"ubuntu:22.04\") | `flag.String(\"default-image\", \"ubuntu:22.04\", \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.5 | Define `--namespace` flag (string, default: \"default\") | `flag.String(\"namespace\", \"default\", \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.6 | Define `--graceful-timeout` flag (duration, default: 30s) | `flag.Duration(\"graceful-timeout\", 30*time.Second, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.2.7 | Validate required flags after `flag.Parse()` | Exits with error if missing | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.4.3 Controller and Server Construction\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.3.1 | Import `pkg/workloadmanager` package | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.3.2 | Build Kubernetes config | Config builds without error | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.3.3 | Create Redis/Valkey client | Client connects | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.3.4 | Construct workload manager controller | Controller creates with config | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.3.5 | Create HTTP API server | Server creates with routes | 0.5h |\n\n### 4.4.4 Graceful Shutdown\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.4.1 | Start controller in goroutine | Controller starts | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.4.2 | Start HTTP server in goroutine | Server starts | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.4.3 | Set up signal handler | `signal.SetupSignalHandler()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.4.4 | Implement graceful shutdown for both components | Both shutdown cleanly | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` compiles and runs with flag parsing.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.5 — Picod Binary Entry Point\n\n### 4.5.1 Directory and File Structure\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.1.1 | Ensure `cmd/picod/` directory exists | `ls cmd/picod/` succeeds | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.1.2 | Create `cmd/picod/main.go` | File compiles | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.5.2 Flag Parsing\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.2.1 | Define `--port` flag (int, default: 8080) | `flag.Int(\"port\", 8080, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.2.2 | Define `--workspace` flag (string, default: \".\") | `flag.String(\"workspace\", \".\", \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.2.3 | Define `--read-header-timeout` flag (duration, default: 10s) | `flag.Duration(\"read-header-timeout\", 10*time.Second, \"...\")` | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.5.3 Workspace Resolution\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.3.1 | Resolve workspace to absolute path | `filepath.Abs(*workspace)` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.3.2 | Create workspace directory if not exists | `os.MkdirAll(workspace, 0755)` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.3.3 | Handle directory creation errors | Logs fatal error on failure | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.5.4 Server Construction\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.4.1 | Import `pkg/picod` package | Import resolves | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.4.2 | Create picod Config struct from flags | Config populated | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.4.3 | Construct picod server | `picod.NewServer(config)` | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.4.4 | Create HTTP server with ReadHeaderTimeout | `&http.Server{ReadHeaderTimeout: *readHeaderTimeout}` | 0.25h |\n\n### 4.5.5 Graceful Shutdown\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.5.1 | Start server in goroutine | `go server.ListenAndServe()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.5.2 | Set up signal handler | `signal.SetupSignalHandler()` | 0.25h |\n| 4.5.5.3 | Implement graceful shutdown | `server.Shutdown(ctx)` with timeout | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** `cmd/picod/main.go` compiles and runs with flag parsing.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.6 — Build Verification\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.6.1 | Verify `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` succeeds | Binary builds | 0.25h |\n| 4.6.2 | Verify `go build ./cmd/router/...` succeeds | Binary builds | 0.25h |\n| 4.6.3 | Verify `go build ./cmd/workload-manager/...` succeeds | Binary builds | 0.25h |\n| 4.6.4 | Verify `go build ./cmd/picod/...` succeeds | Binary builds | 0.25h |\n| 4.6.5 | Test `--help` on all binaries | Each prints usage | 0.25h |\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build all binaries\ngo build -o bin/agentd ./cmd/agentd\ngo build -o bin/router ./cmd/router\ngo build -o bin/workload-manager ./cmd/workload-manager\ngo build -o bin/picod ./cmd/picod\n\n# Verify help output\n./bin/agentd --help\n./bin/router --help\n./bin/workload-manager --help\n./bin/picod --help\n\n# Quick smoke test (will fail without deps, but verifies startup)\ntimeout 2 ./bin/picod --port=18080 2>&1 || true\ntimeout 2 ./bin/agentd --sync-period=1s 2>&1 || true\n```\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `cmd/agentd/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n- [ ] `cmd/router/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n- [ ] `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n- [ ] `cmd/picod/main.go` — Binary entry point with flags and graceful shutdown\n- [ ] `pkg/common/signal` — Shared signal handling package\n- [ ] `pkg/common/version` — Shared version package\n- [ ] All 4 binaries compile successfully\n- [ ] All 4 binaries print help with `--help`\n- [ ] All 4 binaries handle SIGINT/SIGTERM gracefully\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- [deployment/design.md](/deployment/design.md) — Build targets and Docker image specs\n- [AR-009/delta-spec.md](/changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md) — Router flags specification\n- [AR-007/delta-spec.md](/changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md) — Workload manager controller spec\n- [code-execution/spec.md](/code-execution/spec.md) — Picod server spec\n- [idle-cleanup/spec.md](/idle-cleanup/spec.md) — Agentd binary spec\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775881919000,"end":1775881919005}}}}
